<L>__{interior laura's hotel room night}
<A>__{laura opening the door, looks down, sees something, bends down to pick it up. straightens up. angle insert a hotel envelope, the hotel lincoln boston, mass. on the letterhead. laura's hands open the message, take out a sheet of yellow legal paper.}
<B>__{angle}
<A>__{laura closes the door behind her, she does not turn on the light, walks over to a couch by the window, sits down, all the while reading the paper by the outside light. she lowers the paper to her lap. angle insert the legal sheet. it reads, handwritten: laura. i'm going to try. when this is over can we go away? joe.}
